&lt;td&gt;address_concretization&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;address_concretization_action&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;BP_BEFORE or BP_AFTER&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;The SimAction object being used to record the memory action.&lt;/td&gt;
