&lt;p&gt;A 0-1 bag problem. And notice that you should &amp;lt;c style=&amp;quot;color: #FF0000;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;ADD&amp;lt;/c&amp;gt; v12, not MULTIPLY, like in the ida......&lt;/p&gt;
