 &lt;h1 id=&#34;changes-of-python-api-in-ida-7x&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#changes-of-python-api-in-ida-7x&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Changes of Python API in IDA 7.x&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&#34;more&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;from-ida-6x-to-ida-7x-there-has-been-lots-of-changes-and-as-a-green-hands-when-i-look-up-at-some-writes-up-some-method-just-didnt-work-out-thats-when-i-knew-that-many-python-api-has-change-from-ida-6x-to-ida-7x&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#from-ida-6x-to-ida-7x-there-has-been-lots-of-changes-and-as-a-green-hands-when-i-look-up-at-some-writes-up-some-method-just-didnt-work-out-thats-when-i-knew-that-many-python-api-has-change-from-ida-6x-to-ida-7x&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; From IDA 6.x to IDA 7.x, there has been lots of changes. And as a green hands, when I look up at some writes up, some method just didn&#39;t work out. That&#39;s when I knew that many python API has change from IDA 6.x to IDA 7.x.&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;website-that-may-help-you&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#website-that-may-help-you&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Website that may help you:&lt;/h4&gt;
